collection.name: Wulfz Official
collection.description:
➡️ [Pupz](https://opensea.io/collection/pupz-official) | [Alphas](https://opensea.io/collection/alpha-wulfz) ⬅️

81.47% / 7033 NFTS staked as of 6/4/2022 (OS holder count inaccurate)

Wulfz are the Genesis collection of the Wulfz ecosystem. When staked, Wulfz earn 10 $AWOO. $AWOO is the token to the entire Wulfz ecosystem. $AWOO can be used to redeem whitelist spots, train (animate) your Wulfz, mint upcoming Werewulfz, mint Wulfz VX, and more! You can learn more about the project in our documentation! https://docs.wulfznft.com

[Wulfz HUB](https://hub.wulfznft.com) | [Website](https://wulfznft.com) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/wulfz) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/wulfznft) | [Rarity](https://hub.wulfznft.com/Gallery)
